title: Can’t Stop The Feeling
lyrics:
[intro] (C)  (Am)  (F)  (C)
 
I got this (C)feeling... inside my (Am)bones
It goes e(F)lectric, wavey when I turn it (Am)on
All through my (C)city... all through my (Am)home

I got that (C)sunshine in my pocket

I can't (C)take my eyes up off it, moving (Am)so phenomenally
Room on (F)lock, the way we rock it, so don't (C)stop
